title: Real Aussie Slots (pokies) Collection (2014) update
description:
Real Aussie Slots Collection (2014) update



A new re-bundle and updated options for the Classic Aussie Pokier Machines/Slots

these are the same you play in the pubs.. real cash emulation not simulated pokies



12 classic machines from 3 bags full and alike
+1 Card Poker Emulator


4 newer Aussie pokies I think from 2011 or 2010 ? like 50 lions


plus Emulated Aussie Pokies for Android Tablet (not as good as the PC real ones
but still fun)

perhaps theres a way to play the mame32 ones on Android tablet even.. not
had a go but should possible as mame apk is available that plays other game
roms


unrar then just copy the follows as per the other readmes
and use the shortcuts to run

tested on XP to Win 8 although win 8 might have issues with sounds etc
on some of them,

Note! if you have a MS mouse and install intelli point software or that new replacement for win 8 keyboard and mouse center.. you can customise the mouse buttons to send SPACE
for the mame game only by making the right key send SPACE.. works a treat..
try it out.. although win 8 version didnt work as yet.. it did with intellipoint


HELP SEED if grabbing
